<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2024</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:51:51 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[This luxury handbag is made from the material NASA uses to collect comet dust]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>太空和时尚爱好者现在拥有一款跨界配饰，这不仅仅是因为上面点缀着一些月亮和星星。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.fastcompany.com/91047739/nasa-used-this-material-to-catch-comet-dust-now-its-being-used-for-a-luxury-handbag"><em>据 Fast Company</em>报道</a>，法国奢侈品牌 Coperni 推出了完全由 NASA 纳米材料二氧化硅气凝胶制成的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4Ftm7Htob_/">Air Swipe Bag</a> 。科学家史蒂夫·琼斯 (Steve Jones) 首次为 NASA 1999 年的星尘任务创造了这种物质，该任务从 Wild 2 号彗星带回了样本。</p><p> Air Swipe Bag 的重量仅为 1.1 盎司，其中只有 0.2% 的物质是有形的。其余的是通过气凝胶数万亿个通道移动的空气。气凝胶以其轻质结构而闻名，在 20 世纪 90 年代获得了最轻物质的称号，第二个版本打破了这一记录。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nasa-is-looking-for-volunteers-to-live-in-its-mars-simulation-for-a-year-172926396.html">美国宇航局</a>此前将这种物质称为“固体烟雾”，一看袋子就知道这种说法是多么真实。 Coperni 的 Instagram 帖子甚至有一位 Instagram 用户评论：“这看起来就像我的烟枪，当它充满烟雾时，我着迷了。” </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="f5aede9867f4469b975d50f42dc67dc9"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4Ftm7Htob_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF;border:0;margin:1px;max-width:540px;min-width:326px;padding:0;width:99.375%;"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:40px;margin-right:14px;width:40px;"></div><div style="display:flex;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;margin-bottom:6px;width:100px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;width:60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding:19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block;height:50px;margin:0 auto 12px;width:50px;"></div><div style="padding-top:8px;"><div style="color:#3897f0;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;">在 Instagram 上查看这篇文章</div></div><div style="padding:12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display:flex;margin-bottom:14px;"><div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;margin-right:14px;margin-left:2px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;"></div></div><div style="margin-left:8px;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:20px;width:20px;"></div><div style="width:0;height:0;border-top:2px solid transparent;border-left:6px solid #f4f4f4;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;"></div></div><div style="margin-left:auto;"><div style="width:0px;border-top:8px solid #F4F4F4;border-right:8px solid transparent;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12px;width:16px;"></div><div style="width:0;height:0;border-top:8px solid #F4F4F4;border-left:8px solid transparent;"></div></div></div><div style="display:flex;margin-bottom:24px;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;margin-bottom:6px;width:224px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;width:144px;"></div></div><p style="color:#c9c8cd;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;margin-top:8px;overflow:hidden;padding:8px 0 7px;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4Ftm7Htob_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style="color:#c9c8cd;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">coperni (@coperni) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote></div><p>虽然气凝胶只是用来制作一个小包，但在这种情况下，它是一个坚固的配件。该物质可承受自身重量 4,000 倍的重量（远远超过这款钱包的容量），并可承受高达 2,200 华氏度的温度。毫不奇怪，当气凝胶不被制成袋子时，它已被用于<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nasas-curiosity-rover-snapped-this-dreamy-timelapse-of-a-martian-day-175701537.html">火星漫游车的</a>绝缘等任务。</p><p> Air Swipe Bag 尚未在 Coperni 的网站上出售，但如果你想要一个如此强大的配件，它可能会花费你的钱。太空旅行和时尚是两件永远不便宜的事情。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/this-luxury-handbag-is-made-from-the-material-nasa-uses-to-collect-comet-dust-135151909.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/this-luxury-handbag-is-made-from-the-material-nasa-uses-to-collect-comet-dust-135151909.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> efa1594b-a1c6-4a76-a62c-765b92b35ab9 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sarah Fielding]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:51:52 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1709819513</ingested><modified> 2024-03-07T13:52:03+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="1046" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F18d88f60-dc89-11ee-bd5d-640a9b12074a&amp;resize=1400%2C1046&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=9a40149078fb769bd412beddf7072eb42993c401" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1046" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-03%2F18d88f60-dc89-11ee-bd5d-640a9b12074a&amp;resize=1400%2C1046&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=3c6b826cf2dbd746af2628fc50b7e3e8b7098486" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Coperni]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A bag in a secure case.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Coperni Air Swipe Bag]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[SpaceX lawsuit claims repeated instances of gender discrimination and basic safeguarding failures]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><em>警告：以下文章涉及敏感问题。</em></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spacex-dominated-private-spaceflight-in-2023-but-its-competitors-mostly-arent-quitting-153050005.html">SpaceX</a>的一名员工对该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/legal/spacex-worker-alleges-severe-sex-bias-retaliation-us-lawsuit-2024-03-06/">提起诉讼</a>，指控该公司支持一名主管，迫使她与他发生性关系。原告表示，她和其他女性员工还不得不忍受质疑她们资历的“侮辱性评论”，她在升职时被男性候选人拒绝，而且当她抱怨工资低于男性同事时，她遭到了报复。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>原告米歇尔·多帕克 (Michelle Dopak) 自 2017 年以来一直在这家航空航天公司位于加利福尼亚州的总部工作。根据她的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/6/24092721/spacex-lawsuit-sexual-bias-harassment-pay-inequity">申诉</a>，她在就业初期就经历了歧视，当时她被外部男性候选人放弃了工作机会。据称，她的男同事也散布有关女同事的谣言，声称她们只是因为外表才得到工作。多帕克和她的两名女同事会见了格温·肖特韦尔，抱怨这两个问题——“SpaceX 的男同事或员工都不会觉得有必要采取这种行动来证明他们的招聘合理性并停止这种歧视行为，”诉讼称。然而，SpaceX 总裁显然没有采取任何行动。</p><p> 2019年重组后，原告被置于一名男老板的监管之下，据称该男老板向她施压，迫使她发生持续数年的性关系。当她怀孕时，她说她的已婚主管愿意给她 10 万美元让她堕胎，但她拒绝了。她还指控 SpaceX 与她的老板勾结，从他的名下转让了 48,289 股价值 3,718,253 美元的股票，以便他可以逃避支付子女抚养费。</p><p>她的抱怨还没有结束。在晋升到她多年来一直追求的职位后，她发现同时受聘的一名男同事的工资多了 5,000 美元。与她谈论薪酬差距的公司管理人员无法证明这一点，据称如果她也减少股票福利，他们只愿意多给她 2,500 美元。原告在诉讼中表示，这一提议是“一个信息，如果你向 SpaceX 投诉，我们只会对你进行报复，并找到其他方式来惩罚你。”</p><p>该诉讼指控 SpaceX 强迫提出性骚扰和歧视指控的女性员工将其指控提交仲裁，以便对公众保密。 “SpaceX 还试图胁迫（原告）仅将其索赔提交仲裁，尽管此类索赔被禁止强制仲裁，”诉状继续说道。</p><p>原告要求获得一般性、补偿性和后果性损害赔偿，包括工资、收入和其他雇员福利损失。她还要求法院禁止 SpaceX 继续任何“不公平和非法的商业行为”。 SpaceX 目前正<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/legal/spacex-sued-by-engineer-claiming-underpayment-women-minorities-2023-10-05/">面临另一项拟议的集体</a>诉讼，该诉讼声称其支付给女性和少数族裔员工的工资比支付给白人男性员工的工资少了数万美元。一月份，美国国家劳工关系委员会也对 SpaceX <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nlrb-accuses-spacex-of-illegally-firing-workers-for-criticizing-elon-musk-075244828.html?_fsig=duW5Yiq69tCQ91N3xcutzQ--%7EA">提出投诉</a>，指控该公司非法解雇了一群工程师，这些工程师批评埃隆·马斯克在 X 上就针对他的不当性行为指控开粗俗的玩笑。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/spacex-lawsuit-claims-repeated-instances-of-gender-discrimination-and-basic-safeguarding-failures-133014753.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/spacex-lawsuit-claims-repeated-instances-of-gender-discrimination-and-basic-safeguarding-failures-133014753.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cb44b2fb-fa89-4133-a7a2-1e03d0c6de4f</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mariella Moon]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:30:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1709814587</ingested><modified> 2024-03-07T12:29:52+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Society & Culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[Employment & Career]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language